snippet.title: Driftmoon Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Set out on a fantastic adventure at: http://www.instantkingdom.com/

Driftmoon is an adventure-roleplaying game, full of exploration, smiles and surprises, captivating stories and quests, charming characters, and countless delightful details.

This is the Official Driftmoon Launch Trailer (February 26. 2013!)

Music by Gareth Meek
Soundtrack available at: http://garethmeekcompositions.bandcamp.com/
